OL,3,C'I can see your legs': Rioter found
OL,4,Chiding in loft jailed
OL,6,F'Get down now': Bodycam footage shows
OL,7,Fthe moment Lewis Merritt was arrested
OL,9,FA man who was found hiding in a loft
OL,10,Fafter taking part in rioting in
OL,11,FRotherham has been jailed.
OL,13,FBodycam footage released by South
OL,14,FYorkshire Police shows the moment an
OL,15,Fofficer told Lewis Merritt "I can see
OL,16,Fyour legs" as he attempted to evade
OL,17,Farrest.
