OL,3,C'I can see your legs': Rioter found
OL,4,Chiding in loft jailed
OL,6,FThe 27-year-old had thrown chairs and
OL,7,Fplanks of wood at officers who were
OL,8,Fprotecting the Holiday Inn Express
OL,9,Fhotel in Manvers on Sunday 4 August.
OL,11,FHe was traced to an address in
OL,12,FMexborough 11 days later, but police
OL,13,Fwere forced to break in through the
OL,14,Fdoor when there was no answer.
OL,16,FThe bodycam footage shows officers at
OL,17,Fthe mouth of the loft hatch, with one
OL,18,Fshouting: "Get down now. I can see
OL,19,Fyour legs."
