OL,3,C'I can see your legs': Rioter found
OL,4,Chiding in loft jailed
OL,6,FIn response to a comment from Merritt
OL,7,Fhe adds: "Yes, I'm here for you."
OL,9,FMerritt is then handcuffed and
OL,10,Farrested, before being charged with
OL,11,Fviolent disorder.
OL,13,FSheffield Crown Court heard he was
OL,14,Fcaptured on video loitering around the
OL,15,Farea where the riot took place before
OL,16,Fbecoming involved in ugly scenes.
OL,18,FAs well as throwing missiles at
OL,19,Fpolice, he kicked a police van and
OL,20,Fmoved barriers put in place to control
OL,21,Fcrowds.
