OL,3,C'I can see your legs': Rioter found
OL,4,Chiding in loft jailed
OL,6,FHundreds of people had turned up to
OL,7,Fprotest outside the hotel, where
OL,8,Fasylum seekers were being housed. The
OL,9,Fbuilding's windows were later smashed
OL,10,Fand a bin was set alight and forced
OL,11,Fagainst the walls as trouble flared.
OL,13,FMerritt tried to hide his identity by
OL,14,Fwearing a face covering during the
OL,15,Fincident, but had already been caught
OL,16,Fon camera.
OL,18,FHe initially gave no comment in a
OL,19,Fpolice interview but later pleaded
OL,20,Fguilty to violent disorder and
OL,21,Fassaulting an emergency worker.
